image_analysis.description: A photograph of a bedroom interior. The walls are painted a vibrant pink with a textured or Venetian plaster finish. A bed with white linens and a green velvet headboard is visible in the foreground. Two decorative pillows with intricate, colorful patterns and pom-pom trim are on the bed. To the side of the bed is a nightstand covered with a patterned cloth, holding a large white lamp with a pleated shade and black trim, a smaller black reading lamp, and various small objects including what appears to be a telephone and some containers. The ceiling is white with crown molding.
image_analysis.layout: Interior bedroom shot, angled from the foot/side of the bed looking toward a corner.

stamps_or_markings: Bates stamp 'EFTA00001109' in the bottom right corner
